kes her job. The subject pronoun \'I\' refers to the woman.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 2','2026-04-20 17:33:49.233035','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(90,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW',NULL,'4.0','Listen to the dialogue:\nMark: Where were you last night, Sarah?\nSarah: I was at the library. I studied for my English exam.\n\nQuestion: What did Sarah do last night?','2026-04-20 17:33:49.258151','Sarah uses the Past Simple \'studied\' to describe her action last night.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 2','2026-04-20 17:33:49.258151','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(91,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW',NULL,'4.0','Listen to the dialogue:\nClerk: Can I help you?\nCustomer: Yes. How much are these blue shoes?\nClerk: They are fifty dollars.\n\nQuestion: How much do the shoes cost?','2026-04-20 17:33:49.262166','The clerk uses the pronoun \'They\' to refer to the shoes and the Present Simple \'are\' for the price.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 2','2026-04-20 17:33:49.262166','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(92,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW',NULL,'4.0','Listen to the dialogue:\nSon: Mom, did you see my keys? I can\'t find them.\nMom: Yes, I saw them on the table ten minutes ago.\n\nQuestion: Where were the keys?','2026-04-20 17:33:49.267991','The mother uses the Past Simple \'saw\' and the pronoun \'them\' to refer to the keys.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 2','2026-04-20 17:33:49.267991','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(93,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW',NULL,'4.0','Listen to the dialogue:\nAnna: Does your brother live in London?\nTom: No, he moved to Manchester last year. He works there now.\n\nQuestion: Where does Tom\'s brother live now?','2026-04-20 17:33:49.273502','Tom uses the Present Simple \'works\' and \'lives\' (implied) to show his brother\'s current location in Manchester.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 2','2026-04-20 17:33:49.273502','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(94,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776754716/ai_q_listening_1776754714732.mp3','3.0','What is David going to do?','2026-04-21 06:59:07.487026',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'marathon','2026-04-21 06:59:07.487026','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,NULL),(95,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776754717/ai_q_listening_1776754716489.mp3','3.0','When is the marathon?','2026-04-21 06:59:07.495549',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'marathon','2026-04-21 06:59:07.495549','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,NULL),(96,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776754719/ai_q_listening_1776754717882.mp3','3.0','What did Emily do last year?','2026-04-21 06:59:07.500110',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'marathon','2026-04-21 06:59:07.500110','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,NULL),(97,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776754721/ai_q_listening_1776754719440.mp3','3.0','How often is David training?','2026-04-21 06:59:07.505123',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'marathon','2026-04-21 06:59:07.505123','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,NULL),(98,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776754722/ai_q_listening_1776754721070.mp3','3.0','How was Emily\'s marathon experience?','2026-04-21 06:59:07.510139',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'marathon','2026-04-21 06:59:07.510139','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,NULL),(99,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1776796942/ai_q_listening_1776796939461.mp3','4.5','What does Emily do for Assignment 5?','2026-04-21 18:42:59.30