o/upload/v1777275493/ai_q_listening_1777275491095.mp3','5.0','What has the teacher been doing while the students have been preparing for the quiz?','2026-04-27 07:39:27.073676',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 3','2026-04-27 07:39:27.073676','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Robert [Male]: Have you been explaining the quiz rules to the students? \nEmily [Female]: Yes, I have been explaining the quiz rules while they have been preparing for the quiz. \nDavid [Male]: That\'s great, I\'m sure they will do well.'),(106,NULL,11,'PENDING_REVIEW','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1777275495/ai_q_listening_1777275493568.mp3','5.0','Which of the following has been given to the students who are taking the quiz?','2026-04-27 07:39:27.099103',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 3','2026-04-27 07:39:27.099103','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Emily [Female]: The students have been given a study guide which has been carefully prepared. \nRobert [Male]: That\'s great, I\'m sure it will help them. \nDavid [Male]: Yes, it has been prepared by the best teachers.'),(107,NULL,11,'DRAFT','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1777275498/ai_q_listening_1777275495700.mp3','5.0','What have the students been doing since they started preparing for the quiz?','2026-04-27 07:39:27.104188',NULL,NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Quiz — Buổi 3','2026-04-27 14:46:47.396500','TEACHER_PRIVATE','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Robert [Male]: How have the students been doing since they started preparing for the quiz? \nEmily [Female]: They have been studying hard and I think they will do well. \nDavid [Male]: Yes, they have been working very hard.'),(108,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','What do people want to keep clean?','2026-04-27 13:22:33.089003','The question requires the reader to understand the main idea of the passage, which is about keeping the environment clean.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:33.089003','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,52,NULL),(109,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','What did people do many years ago?','2026-04-27 13:22:33.107182','The question requires the reader to understand the past actions of people, which is described in the passage using the past simple tense.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:33.107182','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,52,NULL),(110,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','What is the government doing to help the environment?','2026-04-27 13:22:33.111413','The question requires the reader to understand the role of the government in protecting the environment, which is described in the passage using the present simple tense.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:33.111413','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,52,NULL),(111,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','Why are some people using bicycles?','2026-04-27 13:22:33.114582','The question requires the reader to understand the reason for using bicycles, which is described in the passage as a way to keep the air clean.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:33.114582','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,52,NULL),(112,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','What are others using to reduce waste?','2026-04-27 13:22:33.118138','The question requires the reader to understand the method used to reduce waste, which is described in the passage as using bags that can be used many times.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:33.118138','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,52,NULL),(113,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','What has been happening to many species due to pollution and deforestation?','2026-04-27 13:22:52.616953','This question requires the test-taker to understand the main idea of the passage and identify the correct answer based on the information provided.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:52.616953','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,53,NULL),(114,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','What has been created by some countries to protect the environment?','2026-04-27 13:22:52.619953','This question requires the test-taker to understand the main idea of the passage and identify the correct answer based on the information provided.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:52.619953','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,53,NULL),(115,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','What has the government been doing to protect the environment?','2026-04-27 13:22:52.622436','This question requires the test-taker to understand the main idea of the passage and identify the correct answer based on the information provided.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:52.622436','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,53,NULL),(116,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','What has been happening to the air and water quality in some areas?','2026-04-27 13:22:52.625435','This question requires the test-taker to understand the main idea of the passage and identify the correct answer based on the information provided.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:52.625435','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,53,NULL),(117,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','What must individuals, organizations, and governments do to address environmental issues?','2026-04-27 13:22:52.628437','This question requires the test-taker to understand the main idea of the passage and identify the correct answer based on the information provided.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','READING',NULL,'Environment','2026-04-27 13:22:52.628437','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,53,NULL),(118,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1777296212/ai_q_listening_1777296210724.mp3','5.0','What has been used by people to access the internet?','2026-04-27 13:23:56.468302','The question requires the listener to understand the main idea of the conversation and identify the device used to access the internet.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Technology','2026-04-27 13:23:56.468302','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,54,NULL),(119,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1777296214/ai_q_listening_1777296213466.mp3','5.0','What has been invented by Tim Berners-Lee?','2026-04-27 13:23:56.471875','The question requires the listener to understand the conversation and identify the invention of Tim Berners-Lee.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Technology','2026-04-27 13:23:56.471875','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,54,NULL),(120,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED','https://res.cloudinary.com/decqv3ed0/video/upload/v1777296217/ai_q_listening_1777296215982.mp3','5.0','What have many companies been using to advertise their products?','2026-04-27 13:23:56.474296','The question requires the listener to understand the conversation and identify the platforms used by companies to advertise their products.',NULL,'MULTIPLE_CHOICE_SINGLE','LISTENING',NULL,'Technology','2026-04-27 13:23:56.474296','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,54,NULL),(121,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'5.0','IELTS Writing Task 2: Many people believe that technology has improved our lives, while others think that it has made our lives more complicated. Discuss both views and give your own opinion. Be sure to use the present perfect and passive voice in your essay, and include relative clauses to support your arguments.','2026-04-27 13:24:21.689557','This question requires the test-taker to discuss both views on the impact of technology on our lives, using the present perfect and passive voice, as well as relative clauses to support their arguments. The test-taker should provide a clear introduction, body paragraphs, and a conclusion, and demonstrate their ability to use complex sentences and vocabulary at the IELTS Band 5.0 level.',NULL,'WRITING','WRITING',NULL,'Technology','2026-04-27 13:24:21.689557','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(122,NULL,3,'PUBLISHED',NULL,'4.0','Write about a place where you can use the internet for free. What can you do when you are using the internet in this place?','2026-04-27 15:37:36.651191','Write a short paragraph about a place with free internet access.',NULL,'WRITING','WRITING',NULL,'Technology','2026-04-27 15:37:36.651191','AI_GENERATED','MANUAL',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
